---
import MainLayout from "~/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold px-4">About</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 px-4">
    <p class="flex-1">
      Welcome to my blog, where I delve into the captivating world of software
      engineering! I am a 30-year-old software engineer originally from <b
        >Guatemala</b
      >, now embracing the vibrant tech scene in the beautiful city of Paris.
      With a passion for crafting innovative solutions, I specialize in working
      with <b class="text-cyan-500">React</b>, <b class="text-blue-500"
        >TypeScript</b
      >, <b class="text-red-800">Java</b>, <b class="text-orange-600">Rust</b>, <b
        class="text-yellow-600">Python</b
      >, and the art of <b class="text-green-600">CSS</b>.
    </p>
    <img
      class="h-[150px] self-center rounded-full grayscale hover:grayscale-0 duration-700 transition-all"
      src="/ironman.png"
    />
    <p>
      My professional journey has taken me into the exciting realm of <b
        >fintech</b
      >, where I've had the privilege of contributing to cutting-edge projects
      that blend finance and technology seamlessly. Join me as we embark on a
      captivating exploration of coding, where we'll navigate through the
      intricacies of these technologies, share valuable insights, and unravel
      the secrets behind building exceptional software experiences.
    </p>
    <p>
      Get ready to untangle lines of code and unlock the boundless possibilities
      of software engineering!
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
